; Springer (Knight) movement function
; SOURCE: ZIA-0367, page 10
; ORIGINAL: (Δx=±1 ∧ Δy=±2) ∨ (Δx=±2 ∧ Δy=±1) ~ Spr(x,y)
; V0 and V1 are coordinate pairs (x,y)

 | Spr(V, V) => R
V|     0  1      0
K|
S|   2.i 2.i    S0

 | |V - V| => Z
V|   1   0       0
K|   0   0
S|   i   i       i

 | |V - V| => Z
V|   1   0       1
K|   1   1
S|   i   i       i

 | (Z = 1) & (Z = 2) | (Z = 2) & (Z = 1) => R
V|   0         1         0         1       0
K|
S|   i         i         i         i      S0

END
